channel.title: Help With Godwars on a 317 Server
channel.description: Hello guys, and girls, I've been working and coding my own runescape private server for a couple of weeks now, and I have fallen into a problem, I do not have godwars. I was wondering if ANY body knows how to add Godwars to a 317 private server. I am willing to give you my TeamViewer info, therefore you can show, and do it for me, since I have no clue what I would be doing. I've tried using Cocoa's post about it, but I kept coming up with 100+ errors while I complied it. I had over-checked to make sure I did everything correctly, but I still could not figure out why I had so many errors. Thanks for your time, and please let me know if you are willing to help me. Thanks again, Lonely Biker.
